{"tid":423760,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【爭取獨立】拒做中央政府打手 加泰地方警察保護民眾","createTime":"2017-10-04T07:32:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-04T19:45:55.000Z","uid":22675,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"38e23d1b81c81bdc50897a869bada2202441320a","tid":423760,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T07:32:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20171002/large/1506944603_312e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171002%2Flarge%2F1506944603_312e.jpg&h=025894e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n西班牙周日舉行獨立公投，加泰羅尼亞警員面對同胞以及中央政府的壓力，不少都選擇站在選民一邊，一個小鎮更有加泰警員出動保護票站，獲居民歡呼支持，警員都深受感觸，忍不住落下淚水。<br />\n<br />\n加泰羅尼亞地區周日多處地方出現緊張局勢，但一眾身穿營光黃背心的加泰警員，就一字排起站在票站前守護票站及選民，站在他們身後的選民無不歡呼拍掌，更有市民上前拍拍警員膊頭鼓勵，有男警員禁不住流下男兒淚，亦有人以帽遮着再單手掩臉，似是在抹眼淚。<br />\n另有地區的票站失守，西班牙國民警衞隊更將選民由票站抬出來，再粗暴地將他拋到地上，有加泰警員看不過眼上前介入，獲民眾大力支持，選民更痛罵國民警衞隊是「法西斯！」<br />\n加泰地區領袖周一要求西班牙，從當地撤走所有國家警察。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20171002/57282602\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20171002%2F57282602&d=uBwHMcDZ1EtZCNzkkw%2BSgb%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=f2569cb1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20171002%2F57282602&h=106b71c5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20171002/57282602</a>"},{"pid":"a35d2d1b998a7cc83c70d6b4f287a24b97b2bfae","tid":423760,"uid":33601,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T07:33:41.000Z","msg":"香港警察就<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ec61d7469b338267a9fa67740fbd1f27b117c61","tid":423760,"uid":91562,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T07:45:25.000Z","msg":"對比香港<br />\n我有啲眼濕濕"},{"pid":"04fefb2c8d678d5b227a3573dbd9